data.description: Move-in Ready!  This home is located in the highly desirable Lakes of Summerville community.  Convenient to shopping, dining and hospitals.  This beauty was not only lovingly maintained, but has also just received fresh paint and laminate flooring for it's new owners! The master bedroom is downstairs.  How convenient.... There are three spacious bedrooms upstairs.  This open floor-plan is perfect for entertaining.  As a bonus, the patio has a gas line already ran and ready for you to set up your grill.  The back yard is spacious with the view of the pond.
